
The Harvester class embodies the cycles of growth and harvest, combining powerful offensive magic with defensive durability. Drawing strength from the land, Harvesters protect and cultivate life while combating Decay. Their abilities, inspired by agricultural themes, include healing and buffing allies, summoning energy storms, and unleashing devastating attacks. Exclusive to Meritheraâ€™s devotees, the class emphasizes grit, resilience, and nurturing strength, symbolizing their divine alignment. Their magic is visually vibrant, featuring golden and green hues, ethereal stalks of grain, and scythe-shaped energy arcs.
